        "text_KpdKVY": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>HELIOCARE 360° is a dermatologist proven sun protection range providing very high level, full-spectrum daily photoprotection against UVA (PA++++), UVB (SPF50+), visible light and infrared-A. With its unique antioxidant technologies Fernblock® & ASPA-Fernblock®, HELIOCARE 360° is clinically proven to protect beyond typical sunscreen, defending the skin from within and repairing damage caused by daylight. <br/><br/>With over 50 scientific and clinical studies, Heliocare helps dermatologists deliver next-generation daily photoprotection to their patients.</p>",
