        "text_MEPHTC": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>BIRETIX is a dermatology-focused range designed to support the management of acne-prone and blemish-affected skin through targeted daily regimens. Combining innovative retinol and antimicrobial technologies, RETINSPHERE® and BIOPEP-15, with clinically proven ingredients including glycolic acid, salicylic acid and niacinamide, BIRETIX helps to reduce blemishes, improve skin texture and support barrier health. The range is suitable for patients with mild to moderate acne-prone skin, post-acne marks and uneven texture, and can be used as part of a long-term maintenance regimen alongside prescription treatments. </p>",
