          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>ENDOCARE is a science-led dermatological anti-ageing brand delivering clinically proven, targeted solutions across barrier support, radiance and renewal, supporting both prevention and correction at every stage of skin ageing. Formulated with expert dermatological knowledge, gold-standard active ingredients and patented technologies, including RETINDUO® advanced retinoid technology and EDAFENCE® anti-pollution technology. The range is suitable for patients seeking to address visible signs of photoageing, dullness, loss of firmness, and fine lines and wrinkles, while supporting long-term skin health and resilience. </p>",
