        "text_kVUJDP": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>NEORETIN is a dermatologist-developed skincare range delivering targeted solutions for pigmentation concerns and uneven skin tone. Combining innovative retinoid technology, RETINSPHERE®, with gold-standard depigmenting ingredients such as Azelaic Acid & Kojic Acid, NEORETIN acts at multiple stages of the melanin production cycle to help reduce hyperpigmentation and promote a more even, luminous complexion. The range is suitable for patients with melasma, post-inflammatory hyperpigmentation, sun-induced pigmentation and uneven skin tone associated with photoageing.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
